      "title": "Britain's decision regarding Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Instead of the GSP Plus relief offered by the European Union, Britain has decided to include Sri Lanka in the New Market Ideas system that Britain is offering to developing countries."
